# .gitignore for 30-days-cybersecurity
# 
# This vault is optimized for Obsidian while maintaining a clean GitHub repository.
# 
# Local-only files (useful for personal research and note-taking) are ignored:
# - Canvas files (*.canvas) — Generated by Obsidian canvas feature
# - Scratch notes — Use scratch/, drafts/, or local-notes/ for experimental notes
# - Temporary files — Work-in-progress notes ending in .draft.md, .scratch.md, .wip.md
# 
# When you click on a link node in Obsidian that doesn't exist, feel free to create
# it locally for graph exploration. If it's not ready for public sharing, the patterns
# below will prevent accidental commits to GitHub.
#
# === USAGE GUIDE ===
# - For transient exploration: Create files in drafts/ or scratch/
# - For canvas diagrams: Use *.canvas files (automatically ignored)
# - For personal notes: Use local-notes/ directory (automatically ignored)
# - For work-in-progress: Use .draft.md or .scratch.md suffixes
#
# All tracked files (daily logs, concepts, tools, summaries) are committed to GitHub.

# --- OS ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini
ehthumbs.db
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# --- Obsidian ---
.obsidian/
.trash/
.obsidian.mobile/
*.canvas
canvas-exports/
obsidian-exports/
workspace.json
*.workspacestate
graph-data/

# --- Editors ---
.vscode/
.idea/
*.sublime-project
*.sublime-workspace

# --- Personal scratch and drafts ---
scratch/
drafts/
_private/
local-notes/
temp/
*.draft.md
*.scratch.md
*.wip.md
TODO.md
notes.md
NOTES.md
SCRATCH.md
journal.md

# --- Accidentally created stubs (from Obsidian graph clicks) ---
URL.md
*.stub.md

# --- Unsanitized captures and raw data ---
*.pcap
*.pcapng
*.cap
*.raw
*.csv
*.json
*.xml
*.log
*.har

# --- Binaries and compiled output ---
*.exe
*.out
*.o
*.dll
*.so
*.pyc
__pycache__/

# --- Archives ---
*.zip
*.tar
*.tar.gz
*.7z
*.rar

# --- Credentials and secrets ---
.env
.env.*
*.pem
*.key
*.crt
*.p12
id_rsa
id_ed25519
known_hosts

# --- VM and lab artifacts ---
*.ova
*.vmdk
*.vdi
*.iso
*.img
Vagrantfile
.vagrant/

# --- Python virtual environments ---
venv/
.venv/
env/

# --- Backup files ---
*.bak
*.orig
*.backup
*.tmp
